[00:38.62]At the moment, he's in Madrid.|目前，他在马德里。
[00:42.31]He flew to Spain a week ago.|他一周前飞去了西班牙。
[00:46.58]He'll return to London the week after next.|他将在下下周回到伦敦。
[00:52.15]He's only forty-one years old,|他才四十一岁。
[00:55.89]and he has already been to nearly every country in the world.|他已经去过世界上几乎所有的国家了。
[01:03.42]Nigel is a very lucky man.|奈杰尔是个非常幸运的人。
[01:07.20]But his wife isn't very lucky.|不过他的妻子运气不太好。
